,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5629c23923cd7f409f7796b9be617bdc1640e6ef","tid":987253,"uid":81894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n久唔久都feel到<br />\n做過body check冇事都冇<br />\n機緣巧合去左專科check先知係一個好罕見嘅病<br />\n叫long qt syndrome <br />\n而家要長期食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"咩病黎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T05:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n久唔久都feel到<br />\n做過body check冇事都冇<br />\n機緣巧合去左專科check先知係一個好罕見嘅病<br />\n叫long qt syndrome <br />\n而家要長期食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>做咩檢查先check 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一次過答你哋啦<br />\n其實當時我媽係外地突然暈左<br />\n送左入當地醫院<br />\n係醫院果幾日佢心跳keep住過百好辛苦<br />\n但係佢哋又唔知點解 只係keep住試唔同藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (當地唔係先進國家)<br />\n我媽覺得唔對路要返香港醫<br />\n當地醫生話咁好危險 但我媽堅持<br />\n返到香港先發現原來係個好罕見嘅病<br />\n簡單啲嚟講係心律不正嘅一種<br />\n身體有某基因令到個人唔係好識係心跳過快嘅時候調返低<br />\n醫生話我媽咁都捱到返香港做手術都算係奇蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來醫生話呢個病會遺傳 隨時病發 所以捉左我去檢查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係呢個病暫時冇辨法根治<br />\n自此我就要長期食藥減低病發風險"},{"pid":"45b215438efa04e5338fb3d496d51f2b1238fd74","tid":987253,"uid":225699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0269aad24e9b69775d965774f7c6423f4cdd4934","tid":987253,"uid":81894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41b1ebd73a16e42ef512ac083e43685731bf8f90","tid":987253,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5629c23923cd7f409f7796b9be617bdc1640e6ef","tid":987253,"uid":8